Renders a full-featured list of 1st class BusinessObjects, complete w/ pagination and optional search/query.
@param {string} boClass - class name of BusinessObject's to display
@param {Perspective} perspective - "list" perspective object driving the display
@param {boolean) enableSearch - if true, a textbox is displayed to allow full text search against displayed data
@param {boolean} enableQuery - if true, a dbui-query-builder is accessible to provide advanced querying against displayed data (forces enableSearch=true)
